The evidence with the title 'Germany breaks renewables record with coal and nuclear power ... ' says May 5, 2017  ... Germany breaks renewables record with coal and nuclear power responsible for only 15 % of country 's total energy  ... Energy transition aims for at least 80 per cent of all power to come from renewables by 2050 , with intermediate targets of 35 to 40 percent share by 2025 and 55 to 60 percent by 2035 . 
